{"word":"G2111 - εὔθετος - eúthetos - yoo'-thet-os - Fit","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὔθετος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eúthetos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo'-thet-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fit</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தகுதியுள்ள, ஏற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"well - placed, fit, useful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; <i>well placed</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>appropriate:</i> - fit, meet.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}